00:06:23.090 --> 00:06:25.321
What's the most challenging
role you've done?

00:06:25.321 --> 00:06:25.820
Why?

00:06:25.820 --> 00:06:27.110
Can you talk a little
bit about that?

00:06:27.110 --> 00:06:29.050
SHAH RUKH KHAN: It's
always the next one.

00:06:29.050 --> 00:06:29.220
Yeah.

00:06:29.220 --> 00:06:30.636
It's never the one
that I've done.

00:06:30.636 --> 00:06:32.936
Because if I've done it,
then it's over and done with.

00:06:32.936 --> 00:06:34.310
However badly I
may have done it,

00:06:34.310 --> 00:06:35.930
but it's no longer a challenge.

00:06:35.930 --> 00:06:38.300
But I find the one
thing that I want

00:06:38.300 --> 00:06:40.560
to do in cinema for
the last 25 years now,

00:06:40.560 --> 00:06:42.190
because I've been
working and I don't

00:06:42.190 --> 00:06:44.820
know how to extend and
give back to cinema--

00:06:44.820 --> 00:06:46.090
Indian cinema, specifically.

00:06:46.090 --> 00:06:48.280
So I want to make
it technologically

00:06:48.280 --> 00:06:50.890
a little more
advanced than it is.

00:06:50.890 --> 00:06:53.460
So what I like to
do is try and do

00:06:53.460 --> 00:06:55.740
films with a lot of
visual effects in them.

00:06:55.740 --> 00:06:57.610
I have a small department
of visual effects,

00:06:57.610 --> 00:07:00.550
and I want to enhance
filmmaking in India

00:07:00.550 --> 00:07:03.380
so that, technically,
we can be at par

00:07:03.380 --> 00:07:05.620
with international cinema--
especially Hollywood.

00:07:05.620 --> 00:07:08.380
And of course, we need
to make them shorter

00:07:08.380 --> 00:07:11.010
and have less songs in them
for people to watch them.

00:07:13.760 --> 00:07:14.270
OK.

00:07:14.270 --> 00:07:18.100
So we'll keep them as
long and no songs in them.

00:07:18.100 --> 00:07:20.820
More songs and longer films now.

00:07:20.820 --> 00:07:23.240
But for me, the
toughest have been

00:07:23.240 --> 00:07:26.375
films which I've
produced, actually.

00:07:26.375 --> 00:07:27.750
Because people
didn't think these

00:07:27.750 --> 00:07:28.958
are the firms that will work.

00:07:28.958 --> 00:07:29.980
A film like "Ashoka."

00:07:29.980 --> 00:07:31.700
I think a film
like [INAUDIBLE]--

00:07:31.700 --> 00:07:33.750
and they all flopped miserably.

00:07:33.750 --> 00:07:36.776
So let me tell you, they were
films nobody wanted to buy.

00:07:36.776 --> 00:07:38.150
There was a film
called "Ra.One,"

00:07:38.150 --> 00:07:42.010
which I made-- which I really
wanted to make so that I could

00:07:42.010 --> 00:07:43.640
advance the
technological part of it

00:07:43.640 --> 00:07:45.070
and a difficult film to make.

00:07:45.070 --> 00:07:46.450
And now this one.

00:07:46.450 --> 00:07:48.340
As an actor, I don't know.

00:07:48.340 --> 00:07:52.230
No role is difficult,
because I don't

00:07:52.230 --> 00:07:54.280
have a method that I follow.

00:07:54.280 --> 00:07:56.700
I just take instances
from life, meet people.

00:07:56.700 --> 00:07:57.800
And I meet so many people.

00:07:57.800 --> 00:07:58.760
I love people.

00:07:58.760 --> 00:07:59.477
I love the hugs.

00:07:59.477 --> 00:08:00.310
I love to kiss them.

00:08:00.310 --> 00:08:02.861
I love to talk to them.

00:08:02.861 --> 00:08:03.360
Yeah.

00:08:03.360 --> 00:08:04.776
We're doing the
kisses afterwards.

00:08:07.920 --> 00:08:09.490
So I just get to know people.

00:08:09.490 --> 00:08:11.330
And then somewhere
down the line,

00:08:11.330 --> 00:08:14.160
whenever a role is given to
me, I kind of take from life

00:08:14.160 --> 00:08:15.350
and use it.

00:08:15.350 --> 00:08:16.910
And sometimes,
it's over the top.

00:08:16.910 --> 00:08:19.072
Sometimes, people think
it's too simplistic.

00:08:19.072 --> 00:08:21.530
But I think it reaches out to
everyone, touches everybody's

00:08:21.530 --> 00:08:23.390
hearts, and people
identify with it.

00:08:23.390 --> 00:08:25.110
So films like
"Chakde" were nice.

00:08:25.110 --> 00:08:27.430
Swades.

00:08:27.430 --> 00:08:28.310
There's [INAUDIBLE].

00:08:33.580 --> 00:08:35.645
I like Don.

00:08:35.645 --> 00:08:36.520
I find him very sexy.

