00:08:54.900 --> 00:08:57.310
So talk a little bit
about the KKR journey.

00:08:57.310 --> 00:08:59.680
How did the IPL
journey all come about?

00:08:59.680 --> 00:09:03.271
I know I've always
seen you in the video,

00:09:03.271 --> 00:09:05.770
always there supporting the
team and they've done very well.

00:09:05.770 --> 00:09:09.300
SHAH RUKH KHAN: And desperately
supporting the team.

00:09:09.300 --> 00:09:12.450
Now, like I said, I
wanted to be a sportsman.

00:09:12.450 --> 00:09:16.190
And this whole thing
started about leagues.

00:09:16.190 --> 00:09:18.840
The three things I really
like-- I like entertainment,

00:09:18.840 --> 00:09:20.980
I like children,
and I like sports.

00:09:20.980 --> 00:09:23.360
These are three things
that really turn me on.

00:09:23.360 --> 00:09:24.730
Nothing else, actually.

00:09:24.730 --> 00:09:26.530
I'm not much of a sightseer.

00:09:26.530 --> 00:09:27.900
I'm not much for travel.

00:09:27.900 --> 00:09:28.824
I'm very boring.

00:09:28.824 --> 00:09:29.740
I'm very, very boring.

00:09:29.740 --> 00:09:32.410
The three things that I like,
is like watching films or video

00:09:32.410 --> 00:09:37.400
games or watching
sports or children.

00:09:37.400 --> 00:09:38.225
I love children.

00:09:38.225 --> 00:09:41.872
So whenever there is a thing
that I can involve myself now,

00:09:41.872 --> 00:09:43.580
because I've kind of
done well for myself

00:09:43.580 --> 00:09:44.960
and I have a little extra money.

00:09:44.960 --> 00:09:48.420
So whenever there's something
I get an opportunity to invest

00:09:48.420 --> 00:09:50.700
in, any of these
things, I always

00:09:50.700 --> 00:09:53.000
do without thinking of
the business aspect of it.

00:09:53.000 --> 00:09:54.880
So business-wise, I don't know
if they're doing well or not.

