bidding was very high.

00:10:31.780 --> 00:10:34.470
Much more than I could
afford or still can afford.

00:10:34.470 --> 00:10:36.210
All the big carpets
were doing it.

00:10:36.210 --> 00:10:38.560
I was awake, and I was
hoping somehow my bid was not

00:10:38.560 --> 00:10:40.420
accepted, because I
didn't have the money.

00:10:40.420 --> 00:10:43.200
So I just went ahead, and
after I bought it also,

00:10:43.200 --> 00:10:46.330
we lost so many hours
and so pathetically

00:10:46.330 --> 00:10:47.740
that it became very sad.

00:10:47.740 --> 00:10:50.241
Business was bad, and the
game wasn't being won.

00:10:50.241 --> 00:10:51.740
And it's been a
roller coaster ride,

00:10:51.740 --> 00:10:56.000
but I stuck around with it for
three years now-- five years.

