and you should
know this-- I don't

00:11:00.876 --> 00:11:03.780
want to sound philosophical and
as if I'm giving you a lecture.

00:11:03.780 --> 00:11:07.320
But just when you think
things are going to go wrong,

00:11:07.320 --> 00:11:09.600
if you hold onto them,
they kind of turn around.

00:11:09.600 --> 00:11:12.074
Just that last brink is
always the most important one.

00:11:17.302 --> 00:11:19.260
SUNDAR PICHAI: You
mentioned education as well,

00:11:19.260 --> 00:11:21.120
and I know you've
done work there.

00:11:21.120 --> 00:11:23.520
What do you think about
where education is in India?

00:11:23.520 --> 00:11:25.649
There's so many young
students coming through.

00:11:25.649 --> 00:11:27.190
How do you think
technology can help?

00:11:27.190 --> 00:11:29.875
This is what a lot
of us work on, so.

00:11:29.875 --> 00:11:31.250
SHAH RUKH KHAN:
You know, I don't

00:11:31.250 --> 00:11:33.458
think there's anything more
important than education.

00:11:33.458 --> 00:11:37.230
And I'm very keen that my
kids are very educated.

00:11:37.230 --> 00:11:39.840
And now, with technology
and this accessibility.

00:11:39.840 --> 00:11:41.590
And you know,
education has become--

00:11:41.590 --> 00:11:42.660
there used to be a time.

00:11:42.660 --> 00:11:48.264
And still is, I'm sure, to
specifically specialize in XYZ.

00:11:48.264 --> 00:11:50.430
You have to be a scientist,
you have to be a doctor,

00:11:50.430 --> 00:11:52.952
you have to be an engineer,
and those things are important.

00:11:52.952 --> 00:11:54.410
But I think the
overall development

00:11:54.410 --> 00:11:57.230
happens when you can educate
yourself in a more round way.

00:11:57.230 --> 00:11:59.370
And I think technology
can help there.

00:11:59.370 --> 00:12:01.810
Just the fact--
I'll be very honest,

00:12:01.810 --> 00:12:05.522
and I'm sure everybody
comes in and says that.

00:12:05.522 --> 00:12:06.980
I'm not saying it
because I'm here.

00:12:06.980 --> 00:12:08.990
But feel I don't need
a teacher or books

00:12:08.990 --> 00:12:10.310
since Google has been there.

00:12:15.960 --> 00:12:18.390
I find myself so
much more educated

00:12:18.390 --> 00:12:21.170
in the last few years
because of Google.

00:12:21.170 --> 00:12:23.840
I've got a yearning
for learning.

00:12:23.840 --> 00:12:25.030
I really do.

00:12:25.030 --> 00:12:30.040
And some of it, there's a
church next to my house which

00:12:30.040 --> 00:12:34.760
says-- whatever answers
Google doesn't have, God has.

00:12:34.760 --> 00:12:36.220
And it says that.

00:12:36.220 --> 00:12:37.420
Every day, I pass it.

00:12:37.420 --> 00:12:39.390
And I think it's one
of the nicest things,

00:12:39.390 --> 00:12:45.010
and if you guys can extend just
beyond the search engine, which

00:12:45.010 --> 00:12:48.230
my friend there is head of.

00:12:48.230 --> 00:12:50.940
But just being able to give
people more access to more

00:12:50.940 --> 00:12:54.840
subjects and topics-- and make
it fun, which you guys are.

00:12:54.840 --> 00:12:56.520
That floor there
only [INAUDIBLE]

00:12:56.520 --> 00:12:59.300
to step on those things, I
could spend the whole day there.

00:12:59.300 --> 00:13:01.270
I would never enter
into the office.

00:13:01.270 --> 00:13:04.570
But I think technology and
Google, specifically today,

00:13:04.570 --> 00:13:07.600
can really help education
go far and wide to areas.

00:13:07.600 --> 00:13:10.950
Especially in India, because the
internet is still not gone out.

00:13:10.950 --> 00:13:13.430
There are areas where
schools can't be constructed.

00:13:13.430 --> 00:13:16.006
And I think for India,
especially, it's very important

00:13:16.006 --> 00:13:17.630
that the youngsters
are educated if you

00:13:17.630 --> 00:13:18.755
want to change the country.

00:13:18.755 --> 00:13:20.914
Because we have
everything going for us.

00:13:20.914 --> 00:13:22.830
If we are just educated
a little more, or have

00:13:22.830 --> 00:13:24.120
access to education.

00:13:24.120 --> 00:13:26.600
So I would request everyone
who is working at Google,

00:13:26.600 --> 00:13:28.120
figure out something specific.

00:13:28.120 --> 00:13:30.370
Because you have the intelligent
ones, the smart ones,

00:13:30.370 --> 00:13:31.140
and the fun ones.

00:13:31.140 --> 00:13:35.090
Figure out some specific
things for Indian education

00:13:35.090 --> 00:13:37.810
so that it reaches deep
inside the heartland of India,

00:13:37.810 --> 00:13:40.561
because we need kids like
you coming here and ruling

00:13:40.561 --> 00:13:41.060
the world.

00:13:47.890 --> 00:13:51.250
SUNDAR PICHAI: We know you
have a new movie coming out.

00:13:51.250 --> 00:13:52.500
It's not just Shah Rukh today.

00:13:52.500 --> 00:13:55.949
We have two other
superstars to join us.

00:13:55.949 --> 00:13:57.921
[APPLAUSE]

